The Lady Bisons dropped to 2-5-2 overall and 0-1-0 in A-Sun play while the Ospreys improve to 3-6-1 and 1-0-0 in the loop. “It was a tough one for us tonight,” Lipscomb head coach Kevin O’Brien said. “I thought we came out and played really well in the first half.
